R最好睇)<br />\n1. 詢問<br />\n2. 控制，防止逃跑<br />\n3. 搵記者，由記者盤問（811記者問黑警扮示威者咁樣）<br />\n5. 睇證件、影相<br />\n6. 散水，不包圍<br />\n<br />\n721 805 811"},{"pid":"83be648364db4afa731483f64db2b9d46dc306c2","tid":1463684,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57720e9b9e671446042cec84dbbf7999d2f654c3","tid":1463684,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"公安係鬼，打公安又係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:59:51.000Z","msg":"第五炮 尋日個金毛MK仔 唔好以為我唔知你係邊個 一早認證得你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個係打記者同救護既人</span>"},{"pid":"d6bbd1c3e227d76cb5e734da619119f57438a8a0","tid":1463684,"uid":145423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"其實場面中叫得最大聲果d係無乜出手，要打就打完走左啦，問題係有班人打又唔係打，係咁圍住叫人打死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}